@startuml JurisFinder - Shift-Left QA Comparison
!theme plain

title Comparacao: QA Tradicional vs Shift-Left (LEAN)

skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor<<original>> #FFCDD2
    BackgroundColor<<lean>> #C8E6C9
}

rectangle "**PROPOSTA ORIGINAL (5 meses)**" <<original>> as ORIG {
    rectangle "Mes 1" as O1 #E0E0E0
    rectangle "Mes 2" as O2 #E0E0E0
    rectangle "Mes 3" as O3 #E0E0E0
    rectangle "Mes 4" as O4 #FFCDD2
    rectangle "Mes 5" as O5 #FFCDD2

    O1 -right-> O2
    O2 -right-> O3
    O3 -right-> O4
    O4 -right-> O5
}

note bottom of ORIG
  **Problemas:**
  - QA entra so no Mes 4-5
  - Bugs detectados TARDE
  - Custo de correcao ALTO
  - Retrabalho significativo
end note

rectangle "**PROPOSTA LEAN (4 meses)**" <<lean>> as LEAN {
    rectangle "Mes 1\n**QA**" as L1 #C8E6C9
    rectangle "Mes 2\n**QA**" as L2 #C8E6C9
    rectangle "Mes 3\n**QA**" as L3 #C8E6C9
    rectangle "Mes 4\n**QA**" as L4 #C8E6C9

    L1 -right-> L2
    L2 -right-> L3
    L3 -right-> L4
}

note bottom of LEAN
  **Vantagens:**
  - QA desde o Mes 1 (50%)
  - Bugs detectados CEDO
  - Custo de correcao BAIXO
  - Qualidade continua
end note

ORIG -[hidden]down-> LEAN

legend right
  |= Aspecto |= Original |= LEAN |
  | Inicio QA | Mes 4 | Mes 1 |
  | Duracao QA | 2 meses | 4 meses |
  | Modelo | Waterfall | Shift-Left |
  | Deteccao bugs | Tardia | Precoce |
  | Custo correcao | Alto | Baixo |
end legend

footer JurisFinder LEAN - Abordagem Shift-Left Testing | Janeiro 2026
@enduml
